**Overview**

This dashboard displays key statistics and visualizations for Sys User, Sys User Group and SYS User Grmember table, including active and inactive user and user group metrics, VIP user metrics, user distribution by business criticality, role, department, and login activity over time, providing a comprehensive overview of user demographics and activity.
